IN an era where celebrity marriages do not last long, top actress Stephanie Linus and Linus Idahosa’s union could be considered for a case study. At least, they can share their secrets, and hopefully, other celebrities will learn one or two from them. On Thursday, the couple who became one in 2012, celebrated their 10th wedding anniversary with loved-up photos.   Ogunbayo joins the league of 50     Ondo prepares for Asun Carnival     DJ Cuppy unveils future plans   Sharing the photos, the actress wrote: “10 years on, and our fire continues to burn!” Linus proposed to Stephanie on her birthday in October 2010. The couple spent 15 months planning their special day. Their wedding weekend started with a pre-wedding boat cruise with close friends and family in attendance. The wedding ceremony took place on April 21, 2012, at the Abbaye des Vaux de Cernay in Paris, France.